<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>They've been putting on a loved-up display since announcing their engagement in July.</p>

<p>And Brooklyn Beckham's fiancée Nicola Peltz has given their fans another glimpse at the happy couple's time in lockdown with a series of raunchy new snaps. </p>

<p>Nicola, 25, looked sensational as she relaxed on a bed with her shirtless beau in one of the black-and-white images, letting her blonde locks cascade over her shoulder.</p>

<p>Racy: Nicola Peltz looked sensational in a halterneck top as she relaxed with her beau Brooklyn Beckham on a bed in new snaps shared to Instagram </p>

<p>The beauty donned a halterneck top for the image and rested against silk pillows while Brooklyn, 21, laid across the bed.</p>

<p>While in another picture Nicola flaunted her svelte figure as she showed off her taut midriff in a black thong and delicate chain piece of jewellery.  </p>

<p>Nicola also showed that she's been making the most of the downtime and soaking up the chance to relax with a picture of her wearing a white shirt and sitting in bed.</p>

<p>She accompanied the gallery of images, which also included a snap of her brother Bradley playing tennis, with the caption: 'some love in lockdown.' </p>

<p>Flaunt it: The blonde beauty also showed off her toned figure in a black thong and delicate chain piece of jewellery</p>

<p>'Some love in lockdown': Nicola gave her fans a glimpse into how she had been spending the past few months with her snaps</p>

<p>It comes after Nicola shared another series of loved-up snaps of the couple with her beau jokingly pretending to wring her neck.</p>

<p>While in another picture the couple looked on cloud nine as they shared a kiss while in another photo they linked arms while sipping a drink.</p>

<p>Alongside the post, the actress wrote: 'tb to prom night', with Brooklyn commenting underneath: 'My amazing girl ❤️'.</p>

<p>Brooklyn sported a grey printed T-shirt along with a light grey blazer while Nicola kept it casual in a black top with a V-neckline. </p>

<p>Relaxing: Nicola also soaked up the downtime as she sat in another bed while wearing a white shirt</p>

<p>It comes after Brooklyn recently referred to Nicola as 'my wife' in a sweet Instagram post last month, appearing to confirm speculation they have already married in secret.  </p>

<p>The photographer set tongues wagging when he showed off a gold band on his wedding finger, with his followers asking if the pair had already married in secret.</p>

<p>Appearing to confirm the union, the son of David and Victoria Beckham, commented 'my wife' on a smitten snap of the pair - which Nicola had captioned 'My forever'.</p>

<p>Couple: Brooklyn and Nicola also put on a loved-up display in a series of snaps taken as they enjoyed a drink</p>

<p>Date night: Nicola posted the photos to her Instagram account which saw Brooklyn jokingly pretend to wring her neck.</p>

<p>Wedding speculation started last month when Nicola shared a cryptic snap of a gold ring on Brooklyn's finger. </p>

<p>The image shared to Nicola's Instagram Stories showed the couple clutching a label, with Brooklyn sporting a gold band on his left hand.   </p>

<p>Brooklyn's mother Victoria then uploaded a snap of her son alongside his younger brother Cruz, 15, with a gold ring visible on his wedding finger.</p>

<p>Looking good: Brooklyn sported a grey printed T-shirt along with a light grey blazer while Nicola kept it casual in a black top with a V-neckline</p>

<p>Romance: Alongside the post, the actress wrote: 'tb to prom night', with Brooklyn commenting underneath: 'My amazing girl ❤️'</p>

<p>Brooklyn took to Instagram in July to announce his engagement to Nicola following reports he had popped the question to his 'soulmate' after just eight months of dating.</p>

<p>Sharing a stunning snap of the couple, he wrote: 'Two weeks ago I asked my soulmate to marry me and she said yes xx</p>

<p>'I am the luckiest man in the world. I promise to be the best husband and the best daddy one day. I love you baby xx.'</p>

<p>MailOnline contacted representatives at the time. </p>

<p>Sweet: Brooklyn took to Instagram in July to announce his engagement to Nicola following reports he had popped the question to his 'soulmate' after just eight months of dating </p>
